        <h2>Admirable Qualities</h2>
        <p>Srinivasa Ramanujan, a self-taught mathematical genius, possessed extraordinary qualities that continue to inspire:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Intuitive Insights:</strong> Ramanujan had a unique ability to see mathematical patterns and relationships intuitively.</li>
            <li><strong>Dedication:</strong> Despite facing numerous challenges, Ramanujan remained dedicated to his passion for mathematics.</li>
            <li><strong>Persistence:</strong> His relentless pursuit of knowledge and solutions led to groundbreaking discoveries in mathematics.</li>
        </ul>

